{"tid":2158933,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如果民意叫泛民杯葛總辭，泛民唔肯，會唔會變成咁","createTime":"2020-08-16T04:27:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T05:56:34.000Z","uid":94771,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"52aac13461ab5d79636b950fd29f60e0fd6454c1","tid":2158933,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T04:27:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/trAik17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtrAik17.jpg&h=63cf6319&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qyd4gA5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQyd4gA5.jpg&h=56c3d2e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>定係泛民會同黑警合作，到時將抗爭者掉返入垃圾桶</strong><br />\n<br />\n雖然唔想咁講，如果泛民坦坦白白認返入去臨立會係為資源，為自己個黨生存唔會因為無錢被滅黨，無奈下就算要食屎含撚都要碌返入去的<br />\n<br />\n我反而接受，但唔好再用道德同抗爭做籍口返入去得唔得，好撚嘔心<br />\n唔好再講咩資源幫手足，事實上有幾多係幫手足大家心中有數<br />\n<br />\n蒙面法上訴，眾籌<br />\n議助，黨內自己人<br />\n私人檢控，眾籌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地係臨立會拉一拉布，先唔講到時係奶共派睇住黎剪，只要黨媒一吹風話你地拉布犯黨安法，你地已經無得玩<br />\n<br />\n即係所謂拉布就只係協助奶共派合演的一場戲"},{"pid":"f172a3650b00a201c3afde67676115fcf8bcc6d8","tid":2158933,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T04:28:53.000Z","msg":"飯民要養助理關我事咩"},{"pid":"cfb5b86596fdcf067530c52779d2155a4b795558","tid":2158933,"uid":279333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T04:29:06.000Z","msg":"忠誠反對派<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2083b485dc97d702f898ca04d13aac5b76cfd441","tid":2158933,"uid":94771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f172a3650b00a201c3afde67676115fcf8bcc6d8","tid":2158933,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T04:28:53.000Z","msg":"飯民要養助理關我事咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T04:29:55.000Z","msg":"唔關的<br />\n依家基本上係真係睇泛民真心為香港民主，定係撐民主只係為食民主飯"},{"pid":"32dbac8e4d18f7f03974d1f8356094634b1fba26","tid":2158933,"uid":359022,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T04:32:15.000Z","msg":"李柱銘：強烈反對臨立會，臨時就不用選舉產生嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2158925\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2158925</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正視聽 臨立會係非法 <br />\n泛民根本唔應該接受「非法延任」"},{"pid":"309c319c1f40bb03d6429ae98b6d558f2974a96f","tid":2158933,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T04:33:47.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"866f590380e3226effb94757a5a6b5e40b9db188","tid":2158933,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T04:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c5ab9c0570c02d0340dc5ff06776d61c6d2c2ee","tid":2158933,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T04:36:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73afc7697fdb364d403d4296bccd37cf4dc0d9b6","tid":2158933,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T04:37:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔想咁諗，但覺得最後泛民一定唔理人民的聲音照衝入去"},{"pid":"2e5933e5d4d123946df1a24ace5132ddc104e1eb","tid":2158933,"uid":111934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T04:37:37.000Z","msg":"泛民根本一開始就唔鍾意勇武抗爭<br />\n所以由佢地話會出手幫手足<br />\n真係聽下就算"},{"pid":"c65514370dd89f21bf862257ea200b4532e3a432","tid":2158933,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T05:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkg